<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_417_r1l2"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> freund / Als Jr vns <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> vnd gebeten </del> habt / 
<del rend="strikethrough"> daʒ </del> von des tags </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_417_r1l3">
<del rend="strikethrough">vvir vnſer <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> Erſamkeit </del> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> als Jr mit <expan>Erking<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Sawnſh<ex>eim</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_417_r1l4"><expan>ſüche<ex>n</ex></expan> ſüllt cʒü <expan>winſh<ex>eim</ex></expan> / vnd <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>t</expan> / daʒ wir ew <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_417_r1l5">darauf <expan>ſchicke<ex>n</ex></expan> / Daſſelb <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> tün </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_417_r1l6">vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ewr <expan>fruntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> / . Ob <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> tag abgieng / daʒ Jr vns das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_417_r1l7">cʒeitlich <expan>wiſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> lıeſſet / . vnd vvo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> in den vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_417_r1l8"><expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſach<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / lıeb / dinſt vnd <expan>fruntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>beweiſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan> / Das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_417_r1l9"><expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica</expan> . <expan>Jnuocau<ex>i</ex><hi rend="sup">t</hi></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_417" id="208r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
